I think it a very good idea to have the fences taken down in front - where the badge is - and the metal gate put up. Both gates. Will you look into this for me and see what it will cost? I'd like to have it done any time. That will make a difference. I forget whether or not you have the iron gete, but I seem to remember that you have. If not, of course that must go in too at the same time. I'll send money for this when you tell me how much. You must not be cramped for money in doing the little things around your place that would give you pleasure. Tell me about such things. 
Endless love, 
Jno
Mona's mother arrived last evening. She's considerably older and not happy at all, but she doesn't talk unhappiness. She's a lovable woman - still wrong in ways no doubt - who isn't? but her meanings, I think are all good. Anyway, I made her feel welcome, and shall keep on doing so. 
